      "text": "Yang and his technicians have recovered three dozens of tactical weapons, all in the fifty kiloton range, including some that Colonel Haust's personnel attempted to steal before we stopped him.\n\nThe documentation recovered also has the data for the weapons tests conducted by House [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHouseMadeira],Madeira]]'s research and development team.",
